OL,3,CKnife crime campaigner Pooja Kanda
OL,4,Cgiven OBE in King's Birthday honours
OL,6,FPooja Kanda has been made an Officer
OL,7,Fof the Order of the British Empire
OL,8,F(OBE) following her tireless campaign
OL,9,Ffor changes in the law after her 16-
OL,10,Fyear-old son Ronan was murdered with a
OL,11,Fninja sword yards away from his
OL,12,FWolverhampton home.
OL,14,FMs Kanda said she was "grateful" and
OL,15,F"overwhelmed" by the honour following
OL,16,Fthe death of her son in June 2022.
OL,18,FThe 48-year-old said: "The day I heard
OL,19,Fabout the OBE, I held his picture. I
OL,20,Fshed tears.
OL,26,@zD@WOU
