OL,3,CKnife crime campaigner Pooja Kanda
OL,4,Cgiven OBE in King's Birthday honours
OL,6,F"During that court case, the
OL,7,Frevelation each day was: how is this
OL,8,Fpossible?" Ms Kanda said.
OL,10,F"How? How on earth are these types of
OL,11,Fweapons still available?
OL,13,F"No wonder my son didn't stand a
OL,14,Fchance."
OL,16,FMs Kanda and her family began the
OL,17,FJustice For Ronan Kanda campaign after
OL,18,Fhis death and have since advocated for
OL,19,Fchanges in the law around the sale of
OL,20,Fknives.
