OL,3,CKnife crime campaigner Pooja Kanda
OL,4,Cgiven OBE in King's Birthday honours
OL,6,FShe said one of Ronan's killers had
OL,7,Fbeen able to get weapons online "as
OL,8,Feasily as getting bread and milk".
OL,10,FThe Kanda family's campaigning has
OL,11,Falready achieved one of its goals `
OL,12,Fthe passing of Ronan's Law which will
OL,13,Fmake it illegal to own, sell, make or
OL,14,Fimport ninja swords in the UK from
OL,15,FAugust 1.
OL,17,FPat McFadden, MP for Wolverhampton
OL,18,FSouth East, Ronan's constituency,
OL,19,Fthanked Ms Kanda and her family for
OL,20,Ftheir efforts when the law was
OL,21,Fapproved in Parliament on April 30.
