OL,6,FBut for Ms Kanda, there is still "so
OL,7,Fmuch to do".
OL,9,F"This is just one fight for me," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"There were many failures that I
OL,13,Fendured, and many failures need to be
OL,14,Fturned into learnings."
